headline: Mission Produce's Revenues Up 10%: Start of a Multi-Segment Growth?
summary: AVO's 10% revenue rebound reflects stronger avocado volumes and rising blueberries and mangoes, raising questions about durable multi-segment growth.

headline: Analysts Estimate Corteva, Inc. (CTVA) to Report a Decline in Earnings: What to Look Out for
summary: Corteva, Inc. (CTVA) doesn't possess the right combination of the two key ingredients for a likely earnings beat in its upcoming report. Get prepared with the key expectations.
